Big Brother Naija housemate, Eric has said his love interest, Lilo, who was evicted on Sunday made him look stupid because she was too smart. The Edo born in a conversation with Brighto said he will definitely look for her after the show. He stated that he hopes she is waiting for him because he is not sure of her intentions. “Lilo is such a smart girl, she makes me look stupid sometimes. “I will look for her after the show. I hope she waits for me,” he said. Meanwhile, Lilo in an interview with Ebuka on Tuesday revealed that she regrets her relationship with Eric because he took advantage of her weakness. She maintained that she will be disappointed if Eric pursues a relationship with another housemate. 